special_powers.name: HEY! YOU CAN'T LEAVE YET, THE FUN JUST STARTED!
special_powers.description: Running Shot. // Opposing characters within range can't be placed.

special_powers.name: DON'T WORRY...I KNOW WHAT I'M DOING...I THINK!
special_powers.description: Penetrating/Psychic Blast. POWER: Unequip all opposing characters within range.

special_powers.name: HAHA! STOP! THAT TICKLES!
special_powers.description: STOP. Impervious. // Opposing characters within range can't deal penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: TWO STOP CLICKS IN A ROW??? REAL ORIGINAL...
special_powers.description: STOP. Probability Control. // When this click is first revealed, Doopool can't be healed for the rest of the game. // Opposing characters within range can't use STOP.

special_powers.name: NIMBLE AND DANGEROUS
special_powers.description: When Fire Belly is given a MOVE action and moves 5 squares or less, after resolutions he may make a range attack. // FREE: Place Fire Belly in an adjacent square.

special_powers.name: FIRESTARTER
special_powers.description: Energy Explosion, Poison. // Fire Belly deals penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: TO ENGINEER THE PERFECT WORLD
special_powers.description: Herbert Blackheart Wyndham can use the standard powers printed on his card for lower click numbers.

special_powers.name: OCCULT DEALINGS
special_powers.description: Herbert Blackheart Wyndham isn't a standard character. // Herbert Blackheart Wyndham takes a maximum of 1 damage from attacks, can't be healed, and can't be chosen for Mastermind. Protected: Pulse Wave.

special_powers.name: WELCOME TO THE PARTY...WAIT WHERE ARE YOU GOING?
special_powers.description: Poison. When Deadpool uses it he may treat characters with a Slice of Cake token that are not within 6 squares as adjacent. // When Deadpool hits, give each hit character without a Slice of Cake token a Slice of Cake token.

special_powers.name: FOR ME? YOU REALLY SHOULDN'T HAVE!
special_powers.description: FREE: Choose a character within range and line of fire. Until your next turn, Deadpool can use the EFFECT of any equipment equipped to that character and the chosen character cannot use the EFFECT of any equipment.

special_powers.name: PARTY'S NOT OVER UNTIL EVERYBODY SINGS!
special_powers.description: STOP. Regeneration, Super Senses. // When this click is first revealed, place all opposing characters with a Slice of Cake token adjacent to Deadpool and Deadpool gains Immune until your next turn.

special_powers.name: GOT EVERYONE GOODIE BAGS!
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, give each friendly character a Goodie Bag token and roll a d6. This game, friendly characters have the listed effect: 1-2: Balloons! - FREE: Remove a Goodie Bag token to gain [Wing symbol] this turn. 3-4: Cake! - FREE: Remove a Goodie Bag token to heal 2 clicks. 5-6: Illegal Weapons! - FREE: Remove a Goodie Bag token to modify damage +1 this turn.

special_powers.name: KATANAS AND PINATAS
special_powers.description: Blades/Claws/Fangs. // When a friendly character KO's an opposing character, give them a Goodie Bag token.

name: Wolverine
keywords: Jean Grey School For Higher Learning

special_powers.name: I'M THE BEST AT WHAT I DO
special_powers.description: Combat Reflexes. // FREE: Make a close attack targeting a character that missed Wolverine or failed to break away from Wolverine since your last turn.

special_powers.name: HEALING FACTOR
special_powers.description: Willpower. // At the end of your turn, you may roll a d6 and heal Wolverine equal to half the result.

special_powers.name: BORN TO LEAD
special_powers.description: Leadership. Passenger: 2, but only to carry characters that share a keyword with her.

special_powers.name: LIGHTNING STRIKE
special_powers.description: Energy Explosion. When Storm uses it, opposing characters within 2 squares of the original target are considered adjacent to the original target.

special_powers.name: I'M NOT HERE TO FIGHT
special_powers.description: When Destiny is targeted with an attack, she may replace her defense value with the printed defense value of an adjacent friendly character that shares a keyword with her.

special_powers.name: WITH MY TRUSTY CROSSBOW
special_powers.description: RANGE: Make a range attack with a range of 4 and attack value of 9. Instead of normal damage, deal 1 penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: LEAD BY EXAMPLE
special_powers.description: Leadership, but increases action total by +2 instead of +1.

special_powers.name: KEEP IT MOVING, X-MEN
special_powers.description: When Cyclops hits, until your next turn friendly characters with the X-Men keyword can use Sidestep.

special_powers.name: SAFE FROM CHARLES' REACH
special_powers.description: SAFEGUARD: Mind Control, Penetrating/Psychic Blast

special_powers.name: MAGNETIC FIELD
special_powers.description: Energy Shield/Deflection, Sidestep. Regeneration, but only if Magneto occupies a square with a debris marker. // Modify Magneto's combat values by +1 if he is within 4 squares of a debris marker.

special_powers.name: THE MASTER OF MAGNETISM
special_powers.description: Telekinesis. // At the beginning of your turn Magneto may destroy a square of blocking terrain within range.

special_powers.name: MAGNETIC SHIELD
special_powers.description: Invulnerability, Willpower. // Opposing characters within range halve their range value.

special_powers.name: SURVIVAL OF THE STRONGEST
special_powers.description: Apocalypse has [Cosmic Energy team ability]. // When Apocalypse KO's an opposing character, give him a Strength token.

special_powers.name: MOLECULAR CONTROL
special_powers.description: Charge, Phasing/Teleport, Plasticity. Apocalypse has Giant Reach: X, where X is the number of his Strength tokens.

special_powers.name: PSIONIC POWER
special_powers.description: Incapacitate, Penetrating/Psychic Blast. // Apocalypse has additional targets equal to the number of his Strength tokens.

special_powers.name: THE STRONG WILL SURVIVE
special_powers.description: Invulnerability, Regeneration. // Modify Apocalypse's attack and defense value +1 for each Strength token he has. // When Apocalypse uses Regeneration, you may remove any number of Strength tokens to increase the amount healed by 1 for each token removed.

special_powers.name: LET'S BE HONEST, EVEN I FORGOT MUTANT MAYHEM EXISTED
special_powers.description: Combat Reflexes, Super Senses.

special_powers.name: REQUESTING A WILD CARD TEAM ABILITY PLEASE... WHAT THE HECK IS TEAM PLAYER?
special_powers.description: Deadpool has [Team Player team ability].

special_powers.name: SENTINEL SQUAD DEPLOYMENT
special_powers.description: Each additional XMRF #LG002 Sentinel added to your starting force (beyond the first) costs 25 points. (You may choose a different starting line for each.)

special_powers.name: CAPTURE PROTOCOL INITIATED
special_powers.description: Plasticity, but affects all opposing characters within 3 squares and line of fire.

special_powers.name: ALL POWER TO SCANNERS
special_powers.description: Incapacitate, 2 targets, [Improved Targeting: Hindering].
